<item>
  <title>Was the 2018 Santa Clara Vanguard the most dominant show since 2013?</title>
  <dc:creator>Parker McIlnay</dc:creator>
  <link>https://your-website-url.example.com/posts/santa-clara-vanguard-2018-dominant/</link>
  <description><![CDATA[ 





<p>Was the 2018 Santa Clara Vanguard show, Babalon, the most dominant show in the recent history of DCI? The short answer is no. The 2018 show was by far a fan favorite, and everyone knew who was going to win that year, but it was not very far ahead of 2nd place. I’m going to walk you through why it was not the most dominant show or even the highest-rated show in recorded history. Looking at this first chart, you can see that the Santa Clara Vanguard has never won except for 2018, so they had to have been doing something right that year, right?</p>
